{"title":"Convert letters to UPPERCASE","description":"Преобразовать все буквы в тексте из строчных в прописные или же сменить все буквы нижнего регистра в верхний для всего текста или его части.","content":"## Convert all letters to uppercase\r\nThis tool allows you to convert all letters in the text from lowercase to uppercase, or change all lowercase letters to uppercase. \r\nA change to uppercase for the entire text or part of it may be necessary if it needs to be accentuated. This program allows you to select a section of the converted text, which greatly simplifies the editing of the text as a whole.\n\n You can also familiarize yourself with other functionality of this online [text editor](/en/editor)."}